               <msContents>
                  <summary>The third volume of the <title>Ḥabīb al-Siyar</title> (Beloved of
                     Biographies), uniformly bound with <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_26573"><idno>Persian
                           MS 973</idno></ref>, and probably intended to compliment and complete
                        <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_26572"
                           ><idno>Persian MS 272</idno></ref>. Originally completed by author
                        <persName key="person_45109504" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/45109504/"
                        xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Ghiyās̲ al-Dīn ibn Humām al-Dīn (ca.
                        1475–1535)</persName> known as <addName key="person_45109504"
                        ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/45109504/">Khvāndamīr (1487–1524 CE)</addName>,
                     in <date>937 AH (1530–31 CE)</date>. He presents a general history spanning the
                     pre-Islamic period until the reign of Shāh Ismāʿīl I, which dedicates to
                     then-governor of Herat, <persName role="dte" key="person_f7917">Karīm al-Din
                        Khvājah Ḥabīb-Allāh Sāvajī (fl. early-mid 16th c.)</persName>, hence the
                     title. The entire work consists of a preface, an introduction, three
                     volumes—each of which contains four sections appended with lists of names of
                     prominent figures associated with each period—followed by an epilogue. This
                     volume covers the period spanning the Mongol Conquest in the 13th century until
                     the Ascent of the Timurids in the 15th century. An unidentified scribe
                     completed this volume on <date calendar="#Hijri-qamari" when="1645-08-16">22
                        Jumādá II 1055 AH (16 Aug. 1645 CE)</date>. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_974-item1">
                     <author key="person_45109504" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/45109504/">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Khvānd Mīr, Ghiyās̲ al-Dīn
                           ibn Humām al-Dīn, ca. 1475-1535?</persName><lb/>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">خواند مير، غياث الدين بن همام الدين</persName><lb/>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Khvāndamīr</persName><lb/>
                        <persName type="alt" xml:lang="fa">خواندمير</persName>
                     </author>
